fields.name: Presley Carver Dining Chair
fields.descriptions: An industrial dining chair made from soft faux leather and metal, the Presley displays strong structural design and comfort, all in one. Upholstered in vintage green with a padded backrest and seat, and durable black metal legs, angled for further stability. This is style and functionality for your modern dining space.

fields.name: Neston Armchair
fields.descriptions:
With curves in all the right places, you will sink into the Neston Boucle Armchair. Upholstered in sustainably sourced boucle, this smooth and comfortable design is a statement armchair as well as your go-to seat. Inspired by the retro ideals of smooth lines and soft silhouettes, the Neston in speckled stone is an inviting piece, reminiscent of Luxe 70s Revival design.

For a rich depth of colour and unique softness, our boucle used in this product is not only of the highest quality but it is made from recycled PET yarns so it is kinder to the environment too.

fields.descriptions:

For a rich depth of colour and unique softness, our velvet used in this product is not only of the highest quality but it is made from 100% recycled PET yarns so it is kinder to the environment too.

fields.name: Emile Swivel Armchair
fields.descriptions:
Inspired by the 70s Revival, the Emile Boucle Armchair is a modern take on classic retro style. With curved lines and speckled stone boucle upholstery in natural, the Emile Armchair cocoons the occupant in softness. Finished with a wooden base with a swivel function and stitched finish on the backrest, this chair can be paired with natural wood furniture for that cosy relaxed living vibe.

For a rich depth of colour and unique softness, our boucle used in this chair is not only of the highest quality but it is made from recycled PET yarns so it is kinder to the environment too.

fields.name: Emile Swivel Armchair
fields.descriptions:
Inspired by 70s Revival, the Emile Velvet Armchair is a modern take on classic retro style. With curved lines and luxe velvet upholstery in rich rust hue, the Emile Armchair cocoons you in softness. Supportive, soft, and comfortable with a swivel function, the Emile is fun furniture design at its finest. Finished with a dark wooden base and stitched finish on the backrest, this chair can be paired with natural wood furniture for that cosy relaxed living vibe.

For a rich depth of colour and unique softness, our velvet used in this chair is not only of the highest quality but it is made from recycled PET yarns so it is kinder to the environment too.

fields.name: Sadie King Size Bed
fields.descriptions: A soft and luxurious haven is what your bedroom should be and the Sadie King Bed will have you craving duvet days. It's all retro vibes with this vintage-inspired grey velvet bed featuring a stunning arch headboard with curved stitched detailing in a dynamic semi-circle. In versatile grey, this velvet fabric reaches the floor for a polished look. The rainbow-fluted detailing on the headboard creates a focal point in your bedroom in this highly stylish and functional large bed.

fields.name: Hayden 2 Seater Sofa
fields.descriptions: Contemporary flair with ease, the Hayden Sofa Range offers exceptional comfort and style in one swoop. Upholstered in soft chenille fabric, the Hayden 2 Seat Sofa features seat cushions that are pocket-sprung for a sublime seat. We love the curves and soft lines of this luxurious cream sofa, ideal for modern homes looking for a practical and design-led sofa. And with no assembly, there won't be hours wasted searching for that missing bolt...

fields.name: Wish Wooden Kitchen Stool
fields.descriptions: The Wish Kitchen Bar Stool; perfect for any breakfast bar or kitchen. This Scandic design is practical, contemporary, and stylish, with natural weave seat and black-stained wooden frame. The curved 'Y' shaped back in beech wood and paper cord natural seat showcases Scandi style without compromising comfort.

fields.name: Wish Wooden Kitchen Stool
fields.descriptions: The Wish Kitchen Bar Stool; perfect for any breakfast bar or kitchen. This Scandic design is practical, contemporary, and stylish, with natural weave seat and light walnut-stained wooden frame. The curved 'Y' shaped back in beech wood and paper cord natural seat showcases Scandi style without compromising comfort.

fields.name: Wish Wooden Kitchen Stool
fields.descriptions: The Wish Kitchen Bar Stool; perfect for any breakfast bar or kitchen. This Scandic design is practical, contemporary, and stylish, with natural weave seat and natural-stained wooden frame. The curved 'Y' shaped back in beech wood and paper cord natural seat showcases Scandi style without compromising comfort.

fields.name: Arley Table Lamp
fields.descriptions: Minimal and contemporary, the Arley Table Lamp adds a subtle touch of Scandinavian style with its warm palette and simple design. The fabric shade in soft white and rattan stem combination gives an ambient lighting option and adds a Nordic-inspired accent to your home. Note the brushed brass base for a touch of glam.

fields.name: Lyme Wall Light
fields.descriptions: One for minimalists, the Lyme Wall Light features a matte brass fixture and opal glass shade that adds just enough decadence to your living room or dining room. Easy on/off toggle makes it perfect for bedrooms too.

fields.name: Francia Floor Lamp
fields.descriptions: The soft natural shade with a sleek black stem offers Japandi style with a modern edge. The Francia Floor Lamp sets the mood with sustainably sourced rattan combining this natural conal shade that delicately diffuses the light, reflecting off of the metal stem and base.

fields.name: Denver Metal Floor Lamp
fields.descriptions: A statement piece in your living room, the Denver Floor Lamp radiates warm light into the space, surrounded by its copper shade finish. Reminiscent of industrial warehouses, the shade can be moved to direct light effectively in this retro-inspired design that is ideal for large open plan spaces. With that striking copper finish and sturdy tripod stems, it will become a focal point.

fields.name: Matcha Bouquet
fields.descriptions: The Matcha eucalyptus mix bouquet from Shida adds a contemporary touch to your home. This arrangement is the perfect home accessory, featuring naturally dried, lush green foliage and delicate fresh-looking preserved flowers that are a sustainable and conscious way to decorate your home. The cool hues of the Matcha bouquet can be teamed with vibrant vases for a pop of home decor. Take our Denzal Vase or Cary Vase with Scandi vibes and orange hues. Bringing the beauty of the outdoors into your living space all year round, the Matcha bouquet is handmade per order and arrives ready to arrange in your favourite vase. Gift-wrapped in a flat-packed box, which fits perfectly through your letterbox, making these preserved flowers the ideal, long-lasting accessory for your home, or for a present with that wow factor.

fields.name: The Roar of the Jungle
fields.descriptions:
Exotic, warm and vivid, The Roar of the Jungle Graphic Print is inspired by Asian culture with a hint of post-impressionism art. This print brings the aesthetics of the natural world combined with the imagination, using organic abstract shapes and an earthy colour palette.

Only giclée printing processes are used for this print resulting in the highest quality museum-level colours and sharpness. Choose between a number of different coloured frames and two sizes for the perfect print for your space.

fields.name: Ridley Wavy Full Length Mirror
fields.descriptions: Inspired by the iconic curves and waves of interior design from the 1970s, the Ridley wiggle full-length mirror with a sustainable paulownia wood frame offers tired walls an instant uplift. In a walnut-stained ridged wood design, whether it's within an eclectic mix or a focal point by itself, the Ridley pops.

fields.name: HKliving Glass Vase Dulce
fields.descriptions: The perfect twist between vintage and contemporary, featuring a subtle swirled pattern on a classic shape. This glass vase is sure to catch the attention of the guests while adding a touch of elegance to your home.

fields.name: Athena Terracotta Vase
fields.descriptions: A striking white and black vertical stripe vase that is made for bright bouquets. Ideal for creative, organic arrangements, this classic vase shape features messy organic lines for a freeing and abstract feel. A focal home decor piece whether full or empty, with a narrow neck for keeping large bouquets looking stunning.

fields.name: Cubitt TV Stand
fields.descriptions: The Cubitt Range is a seamless blend of sculptural design and functional furniture. Incorporating soft curves of the solid mango wood for that clean modernist approach, this TV Stand features downward hinged door across the front with brass handles revealing ample space for living room clutter. Elevated elegantly from the floor and stained in a walnut wood finish that makes the natural grains of mango wood pop, combine your dark wood TV unit with soft neutral fabrics such as cream rugs and boucle furniture.

fields.name: Cubitt Chest of Drawers
fields.descriptions: The Cubitt Range is a seamless blend of sculptural design and functional furniture. Incorporating soft curves of the solid mango wood for that clean modernist approach, this spacious chest of drawers with brass handles features three large drawers that are elevated elegantly from the floor. Stained in a walnut wood finish that makes the natural grains of the mango wood pop, combine your dark wood drawers with soft boucle fabrics and cream textured duvet set.

fields.name: Asher Tall Sideboard
fields.descriptions:
70s revival meets classic style, the Asher Tall Sideboard is built from sustainable mango wood in a rich walnut stain finish, highlighting the natural knots and grains of this exquisite wood. The 2 doors feature arched indent detailing and open to reveal ample storage space across three shelves. This retro style is robustly built with smooth surfaces, resting on four wooden balls.

View The Asher Range

Mango trees reach maturity in approximately 15 years making them one of the fastest-growing hardwoods. Towards the end of these years, the tree produces less fruit and can be harvested for furniture, making use of the full lifecycle of the tree. Due to Mango Wood’s strength, it is also just as durable as solid wood.

fields.name: Brentford 8 Seat Dining Table
fields.descriptions: Gather around the Brentford dining table. The table top is made from glass ceramic making it strong and heat-resistant, and finished with an industrial black metal frame to add a very contemporary feel to your dining room or kitchen. With its sleek and clean lines, you'll find the Brentford table will fit into any interior style with ease.

fields.name: Roxby Wooden Bar Table
fields.descriptions: This retro-inspired Roxby Wooden Bar Table has hints of mid-century design in its silhouette to give a vintage 70's feel to your kitchen. Featuring an oak veneer table top with an angled oak wood frame in black, the Roxby is a contemporary and convenient choice; perfect for modern open-plan living kitchen/living areas.

fields.name: Roxby Wooden Bar Stool
fields.descriptions: This retro-inspired Roxby Wooden Stool has hints of mid-century design in its silhouette to give a vintage 70's feel in your kitchen. Featuring a curved oak veneer backrest and seat with an angled black wood frame with footrest, this is a comfortable seat that is easily cleaned and high quality; perfect for student living and open-plan living spaces.

fields.name: Madison Set of 2 Nesting Coffee Tables
fields.descriptions: The Madison nesting coffee tables are a must for the home when you need space-saving solutions with a Art Deco twist. The metal in a brushed brass finish with a white marble top - the Madison is compact and easy to move around any space within your home.

fields.name: Madison Set of 2 Nesting Coffee Tables
fields.descriptions: The Madison nesting coffee tables are a must for the home when you need space-saving solutions with a Art Deco twist. In black metal with a white marble top - the Madison is compact and easy to move around any space within your home.
